The paper deals with reinforcement learning agents operating in a common environment, which is a typical problem in machine learning. The focus is on exploring the environment efficiently, which is a key aspect of reinforcement learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.MA (Multiagent Systems). The paper also deals with robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY) to some extent, which are relevant sub-categories.
